<br>
I propose a new AA.  It take 25 points to obtain this and level 65.  But, when this AA is activated and something hits, it instantly becomes rooted in place.  It can still hit you, summon you and cast on you but it can't chase you now.  This is different than root in that it is not cast but requires you to get hit in order to root something.<br>
<br>
The skill would need a duration of 1 minute, and a reuse of about one minute and 20 seconds.<br>
<br>
Its been 3 years, I think one of us would have figured out how to cast a simple sub level 10 spell that something like 8 classes get. <p><hr>
