  <br>
<br>
Snare on the other hand.  Get a snare off and it's off to the races.  Run a little bit, fire a FOT, send water pet, Run a little bit, FOT, now that would be overpowering.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
